<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>New Booking Request</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      color: #333333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e67e22;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #27ae60;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>New Booking Request Received</h2>
    <p>Hi {{guideName}},</p>
    <p>
      You have received a new booking request from 
      <span class="highlight">{{travellerName}}</span> 
      for your tour <span class="highlight">"{{tourTitle}}"</span>.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Booking Details:</strong><br>
      ðŸ“… Date: <span class="highlight">{{bookingDate}}</span><br>
      ðŸ‘¥ Number of People: <span class="highlight">{{numOfPeople}}</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Please log in to your guide dashboard to review and respond to the booking request.
    </p>
    <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="button">View Booking</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from Journiq. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
